* Gemunu
* Vijaya
* Perakum
* Tissa

==School anthem==

The school song is "Siridula Sinhala Deepe", which is sung at the start of the school day and on important occasions. The words of song were composed by Mr. Doltan Alwis and music by Pandith [[W. D. Amaradeva]].<ref>{{cite web|last1=Official WebSite|first1=PCM|title=PCM Official|url=http://pcm.sch.lk/school-profile/school-anthem/}}</ref>
